\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 So he only had his birthday every four years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 In one period of time it went eight years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 In that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 
That's right. See - every so many years it runs into a number - that's an eight year period. There's not a lot of people know that. No, there's one period was eight years. And it happened to be that he came in that eight years.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What was his name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Frederick Richard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 That was the youngest one - how old was the one next to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well - younger than me - about two years younger. Averaged about two years in between.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Can you remember their names - starting from the top?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Maria, Sarah - Sarah Ann, Martha Fanny, Alfred James, James John, William Henry, Henry Frederick - Frederick Richard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
