hat - 1946. 1926 - about right. Round about that date. Near enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Where did she come from?
