\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 She wasn't a Londoner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Do you know if she had any jobs before she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14370062 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
