\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Yes, she was serving in a public house in Bow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14370062 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 ?
