ur. Although eventually - she did - go father afield, you know, not just the - close neighbours but further afield.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did she get paid for that?
