\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Were the clothes new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12650100\charrsid2513175  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
