\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Out of what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Wood.
