\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What time did your son go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What period of life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Early years. Up 'til 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well - 1918 - well he was only four at 1918. See he was born in 1914, he was only four years of age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 He was going to bed pretty early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well - when it was dark he had to come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did he share a bed or a bedroom with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 He had a bed to himself - was it in your room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 You had two bedrooms in the flat - two bedrooms and a living room was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 That's right. And a scullery of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Was there a room used for bathing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 
Well we did have a bath and then something happened with the people downstairs and had to do away with it. So we had to bath as best we could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 How often was he bathed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well it's all according what state he got in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Where were meals eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Is this the kitchen or scullery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Kitchen. Scullery was another little room on its own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Where did your wife cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 In the kitchen - in the scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Oh what?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Gas stove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you all have breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No. See because I used to have to get up get out just after seven. See and he never used to get in 'til nine - naturally he was after me.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What did you usually eat and drink for breakfast then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Anything that was going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Was it much the same as when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No, better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What things would you eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well we generally had a - what you might call a luxury. See a rasher or anything like - egg or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What did you have for lunch time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you go home to lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No, I was too far away. So was he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you have a cooked meal in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What sort of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What we would have had for dinner. Instead of that we had a makeshift lunch took with us, see, then had our dinner when we got home.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did your wife make bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Now and again. All according -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Bottled fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No. She pickled onions of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Were tinned or dried vegetables or fruit used?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 It's all according what she fancied. I let - see - being the housekeeper she bought what was - what she thought fit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 But you had tinned foods then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Meat - every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Ever tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well there was - wasn't a lot then. Not same as there is now - not nearly the amount.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did your wife ever go short so that you or your son could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Was your son allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Always talking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Would you allow him to leave some food on his plate if he didn't want it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well if he didn't want it he'd naturally leave it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did he have to sit in a certain way and hold his knife and fork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well he was taught the way to behave at table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 When he was young did you feel that there was a right way or a wrong way to bring up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well you brought him up as you thought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you and your wife have the same ideas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Was there anyone you used to talk to if you were worried about your son - did you talk to your mother-in-law or your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 
Well - as matter of fact I never had a mother-in-law. And - I had a mother and father but - what what was to do with them - what was to do with us was nothing to do with them. 'Cos we were different families.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Can you tell me any of the things you felt you ought to do for your children - provide affection or safety or discipline?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well - kept him within bounds. Otherwise we let him do what he liked - practically what he liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 What did you bring him up to consider important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Well - look after himself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 If he did something you disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 He got told off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you ever punish him by hitting him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 His mother used to if he done anything out of the ordinary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Who looked after him when she worked?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 
She was never out when we were - in. You understand what I mean? I don't mean that wrong. Always in and everything was just so by time we got there. A good housekeeper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 When you and your wife were not doing your work how did you spend your time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 When what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 When you weren't working - did you ever go out together in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Not very often - 'cos money was tight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did either of you go to any clubs or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you continue to take part in playing football?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 I didn't but my boy did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you have any interests in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Only looking after it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Any what? Me - no. If anything wanted doing I used to do it. If I was able. Mess it up or sometimes couldn't do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6578641 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 Did you have friends whom you invited in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14877653 JT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 
He used to fetch 'em. Yes, we used to be in there of a night time - listen to the wireless - knock at the door or let himself in. Who you got with you? Oh so and so and so and so and so and so and so and so. Got anything to eat?
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid6578641 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14836025\charrsid2513175 
\par }}